387
00:37:56,274 --> 00:37:57,617
It's all right.
You're fine.

388
00:37:57,776 --> 00:37:59,198
What are you doing?

389
00:38:00,695 --> 00:38:01,696
Jack.

390
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:03,700
Calm down, Yuri, okay?
You're gonna be just fine.

391
00:38:03,782 --> 00:38:06,581
