406
00:38:54,123 --> 00:38:56,467
Your mission is
bleeding out over there.

407
00:38:56,626 --> 00:38:58,754
The mission continues.
We go to the hotel.

408
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:06,140
Come on, let's move.
Let's move.

409
00:39:17,772 --> 00:39:18,944
This is nuts.

410
